		- EventTimes: Thoi gian su kien
			- Time: Thong tin moc thoi gian
				- Day: Ngay dien ra trong thang
				- Times: Danh sach cac mui gio dien ra trong ngay
				- Stage: Hang cua tran (0: Vong hon chien, 1..N: Vong chung ket)
				- IncreaseStageForWinnerTeam: Co tang bac cua chien doi cho doi thang cuoc khong (Tai vong hon chien se khong tang, con cac vong o chung ket se tang de loai truc tiep luon)
	- Award: Phan thuong
		- Config: Thiet lap nhan thuong
			- FromDay: Ngay bat dau nhan thuong trong thang
			- ToDay: Ngay ket thuc nhan thuong trong thang
		- WinRound: Phan thuong khi chien thang trong luot dau bat ky
			- Exp: Kinh nghiem
			- BoundMoney: Bac khoa
			- Repute: Danh vong
		- EnterRound: Phan thuong khi bat dau luot dau
			- Exp: Kinh nghiem
			- BoundMoney: Bac khoa
			- Repute: Danh vong
		- FinalRank: Phan thuong theo thu hang
			- RankInfo: Thong tin hang
				- FromRank: Tu thu hang
